Welcome to AutoHighlight!

Usage
-----

To summarize a soccer video, navigate to video dir and use the following command:

   $ docker run --runtime=nvidia -v $(pwd):/data autohighlight python autohighlight.py /data/source.mp4 /data/summary.mp4

To split data for model training, use the following:

   $ docker run -v <filepath>:/data bash create_dataset.sh

